Roles & Responsibilities
Responsibilities
As an industry expert formulate and execute the growth strategy, pay close attention to each public chain, meme ecological hotspot, open up the synergistic growth of various businesses, and activate the number of wallet users.
Emphasis on user experience, has undertaken the growth of global applications, and has methodologies for user growth in different countries. Define and deliver product roadmap to serve the best experience to both internal and external users while being compliant with required regulations around the world;
Responsible for the growth of the entire web3 product, and coordinate priorities with upstream and downstream teams. Responsible for the design of core product modules;
Define and analyze metrics to guide product development;
Follow up the whole process of projects, collaborate with designers and engineers to develop detailed product specifications, drive global product launches and lead beta programs;
Plan, organize, and deliver new products and features to the market based on global vision and user experience;
Competitor analysis and market research, staying informed of the overall market landscape, including competitors and potential partners.
Requirements:
Bachelor's degree or above
Product development experience in products and growth;
Related working experience in Crypto Wallet Product and/or DeFi portal product implementation;
Familiar with globalization and localization, capable of launching products for global markets;
Good communication, experimental mindset, team spirit: motivated to initiate and lead in a collaborative team;
Able to understand and assess engineering, design and schedule tradeoffs, manage product backlogs with a priority mindset;
Sharp eyes for good design and user experience.
